name: Daisy
description:
A lovely daisy flower hangs from silver chain. Simplicity it self. You'll love it so much you might just wear it everyday.

The daisy pendant measures about 1" across. You choose a 16", 17" or 18" chain.
Please specify your length in the message to seller box at checkout, otherwise I will ship with a 17" chain.

Closed with silver lobster clasp.

This item will arrive in a kraft jewelry box or an organza drawstring pouch suitable for gift giving.

name: Olive
description:
Swarovski pearls in olive below gunmetal ring and simply hooks earwires. Sweet simplicity.
1.5" in total length, very lightweight. 
Items come in a kraft jewelry box or an organza drawstring pouch suitable for gift-giving.

name: Gerbera
description:
I'm addicted to these earrings!

Some days when I'm short for time and don't want to sport a lot of bling, I love a great pair of earrings that can stand alone - like these!

An antiqued brass gerberas hang from hooks earwires. The gerberas measure 1" and the earrings hang 1.5" with the earwire.

This item will arrive in a cotton-filled jewelry box or an organza drawstring pouch suitable for gift giving.
